      "orig": "I recently built a new PC for my birthday and I splurged a bit with a new AMD Radeon 7900 XTX GPU. Although I'm not a heavy gamer, I'm working with  LLMs  more often and I'm interested to do some of this work at home.",
      "text": "I recently built a new PC for my birthday and I splurged a bit with a new AMD Radeon 7900 XTX GPU. Although I'm not a heavy gamer, I'm working with  LLMs  more often and I'm interested to do some of this work at home."
    },
